{"characterId":25}],"windowDisplayName":"燐子","body":"是这样啊……\n那么……我就打扰了……\n……咦？这个香味……是咖喱吗？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":25,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":25,"voiceId":"2022birthdayMemorial-009-004","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":9}],"windowDisplayName":"巴","body":"是的！其实我最近热衷于从香料开始制作咖喱。\n前不久生日的时候，也收到了Afterglow的大家\n送我的香料哦","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":9,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":9,"voiceId":"2022birthdayMemorial-009-005","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":25}],"windowDisplayName":"燐子","body":"从香料开始……制作咖喱……\n好正宗……好厉害啊……！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":25,"motionName":"nnf04","expressionName":"smile01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":25,"voiceId":"2022birthdayMemorial-009-006","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":9}],"windowDisplayName":"巴","body":"明明很简单，在很多方面却又意外的讲究，我觉得很有趣！\n哪怕使用相同的香料，根据比例和加热顺序的不同，\n味道也会完全不一样哦","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":9,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":9,"voiceId":"2022birthdayMemorial-009-007","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":25}],"windowDisplayName":"燐子","body":"总觉得……我能理解这种感觉……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":25,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":25,"voiceId":"2022birthdayMemorial-009-008","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":9}],"windowDisplayName":"巴","body":"燐子同学也会做咖喱吗？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":9,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":9,"voiceId":"2022birthdayMemorial-009-009","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":25}],"windowDisplayName":"燐子","body":"不……我指的不是这个……\n我在NFO里……有过相似的经验……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":25,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":25,"voiceId":"2022birthdayMemorial-009-010","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":25}],"windowDisplayName":"燐子","body":"哪怕是同一把武器……只要改变装备的搭配……\n它的技能和性能也会发生变化……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":25,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":25,"voiceId":"2022birthdayMemorial-009-011","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":9}],"windowDisplayName":"巴","body":"原来如此！\n确实很像呢~！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":9,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":9,"voiceId":"2022birthdayMemorial-009-012","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":25}],"windowDisplayName":"燐子","body":"顺便问一下，今天……你是用什么香料……\n制作的咖喱……？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":25,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":25,"voiceId":"2022birthdayMemorial-009-013","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":9}],"windowDisplayName":"巴","body":"是用香菜籽、孜然、姜黄、辣椒、香旱芹籽\n这五种香料做成的鸡肉咖喱。\n我打算最后再加入烤芦笋，为它增添春日的气息~！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":9,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":9,"voiceId":"2022birthdayMemorial-009-014","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":25}],"windowDisplayName":"燐子","body":"很不错呢……应该会很好吃……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":25,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":25,"voiceId":"2022birthdayMemorial-009-015","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":9}],"windowDisplayName":"巴","body":"啊！对了！\n燐子同学还没吃午饭吧？\n不介意的话，和我们一起吃吧？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":9,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":9,"voiceId":"2022birthdayMemorial-009-016","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":25}],"windowDisplayName":"燐子","body":"可是……\n不会给你们……添麻烦吗……？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":25,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":25,"voiceId":"2022birthdayMemorial-009-017","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":9}],"windowDisplayName":"巴","body":"不用担心！今天爸爸妈妈都有工作，\n由我来做饭。\n所以，如果燐子同学能和我们一起吃饭，我反而更开心！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":9,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":9,"voiceId":"2022birthdayMemorial-009-018","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":25}],"windowDisplayName":"燐子","body":"那我就……恭敬……不如从命了……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":25,"motionName":"odoodo01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":25,"voiceId":"2022birthdayMemorial-009-019","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":24}],"windowD